txt.en: You have completed Gothmog the Dread Terror -- Tier 2
You have completed 'The Abyss of Mordath: The Spoiled of the Eye -- Tier 2'.
You have completed 'The Abyss of Mordath: The Deathless Warden -- Tier 2'.

Determined to wield the lost Ring of Power Manthríf once more, King Váskmun Greytooth has led his Firehorn Dwarves into the Abyss of Mordath, where the sunken foundations of Barad-dûr now rest. Meanwhile, the Order of the Eye has made haste to pursue the Firehorns, eager to avenge their fallen and contest the dwarves' claim to the greatest artifacts of the Dark Lord. Unbeknownst to any of them, greater still are the terrors Sauron hid away in the shadows of the Mordath.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This deed can only be completed on the Tier 2 difficulty of the Abyss of Mordath raid.</rgb>
